      "patchset_number": 7,
      "line": 90,
      "message": "AbstractCDSProcessingBB BPMN is supposed to be called for VNF (ConfigAssignVnfBB.bpmn) as well as PNF(workflow name not known). PNF workflows is not using BuildingBlock design, it does not have BuildingBlockExecution object, they are using DelegateExecution.   Hence as a work around, am getting required data from BuildingBlockExecution and setting it back to DelegateExecution.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 4695,
        "name": "Sunil Kumar Biradar",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "SB00577584@techmahindra.com",
        "username": "SunilB"
      },
      "updated": "2019-03-20 11:53:38.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "2a69b190_1ad92aeb",
      "unresolved": false
    },
